	[li 
		"Genre: Action
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[h3 
	"Stuff to know
	$LF
]h3
[ul 
	[li 
		"Jumping is faster then walking
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"In order to the glitch, Spidey must be standing and not crawling
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[h3 
	"How to do the glitch
	$LF
]h3
[ul 
	[li 
		"Make your way to the foyer
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"Climb up on to the helicopter
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"When the helicopter reaches the bottom, get off.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"If you are at Mysterio's End, climb back up on to the helicopter.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"When the helicopter has reached its peak, jump to the left.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"Hold spacebar and up+left to shoot a web. This will carry to the left easier.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"If done correctly, spidey will be standing up in the wall. If he is crouching, crawl out and try again.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"Press up to fall down through the wall, then pull yourself onto the platform. Make sure you go on to the platform on the bottom (spidey should be upside down)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		"Stand up, walk to the left, stand on the button. The bad guy will fall and the game is complete.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
[h3 
	"Closing Comments
	$LF
]h3
